# {{ .AppName }}

Go service scaffold initialized by `hatch`.

## Quick Start

```bash
hatch tools install
hatch gen ent
hatch env start
go run ./cmd/server serve
```

Common commands are provided by the `hatch` CLI:

- `hatch build`
- `hatch start`
- `hatch dev`
- `hatch env add minio`
- `hatch migrate generate --name init`
- `hatch gen rpc`
